F-FUSION-ATTN-WMMA-WALL -- round 2 of 3 (codegen + ptxas-clean + $0 oracle) -- 2026-05-25
========================================================================================
GPU sec10 moat: Tensor-Core fused flash-attention. The successor to round-1's
naive-scalar kernel (archive/fires/fusion_attention_flash_2026_05_25/) which lost
the wall 1.4-1.5x because its inner GEMMs were scalar fma loops. This round puts
both inner GEMMs (QK^T and P.V) on Tensor Cores via wmma.mma.sync m16n16k16
(f16 mul, f32 acc) with the S tile resident in SHARED MEMORY (never to HBM).

THIS ROUND = codegen + ptxas-clean (3 arches) + $0 structural oracle. The timed
silicon wall (clause b) is DEFERRED to round 3 -- the parent runs timed fires
